page_0: "I have remained strong. My sturdy Hammer companions would not dare to complain or grumble of the stomach flu, so neither shall I. I was able to keep down a small bit of water today - the first time all day. I can't imagine where I would have contracted such a terrible sickness. Perhaps 'tis only the winter weather. I shall sleep for a while and if the illness has not subsided, I will shamefully appeal for help into town for the hand of a healer. But for now, I must rest."